The paper describes an artificial Ant Colony System algorithm to solve combinatorial optimization problems, which involves swarm intelligence and optimization techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Other likely categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
